2020年4月21日，[[香港|香港]][[香港特別行政區行政會議|行政會議]]（事實上的內閣）出現了人事變動。[[香港特別行政區行政長官|行政長官]][[林鄭月娥|林鄭月娥]]進行[[香港特別行政區第五屆政府|上任後]]首次的[[內閣改組|政府改組]]（又稱內閣改組<ref>{{Cite web|title=北京港府宣佈內閣局部改組 民主派批民望低官員留任非向港人問責|url=https://www.voacantonese.com/a/hk-reactions-to-bj-n-carrie-lam-official-announced-cabinet-reshuffle-20200422/5385241.html|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2020-04-22|work=[[美國之音|美國之音]]|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814053205/https://www.voacantonese.com/a/hk-reactions-to-bj-n-carrie-lam-official-announced-cabinet-reshuffle-20200422/5385241.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是[[反送中運動|反送中運動]]爆發後首次有[[香港政治委任制度|問責官員]]下台<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|title=Hong Kong Leader Carrie Lam Replaces Five Ministers in Cabinet Reshuffle|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-22/hong-kong-s-lam-replaces-five-ministers-in-cabinet-reshuffle|date=2020-04-22|accessdate=2020-10-27|language=en|publisher=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|last=Lung|first=Natalie|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026172052/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-22/hong-kong-s-lam-replaces-five-ministers-in-cabinet-reshuffle|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是[[香港回歸|主權移交]]後最大規模的一次。香港傳媒形容是次改組時稱為「大地震」<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://theinitium.com/article/20200422-whatsnew-hksar-cabinet-reshuffle/|title=港府人事大變動，國務院免去5局長職務，原掌中港事務官員平調公務員局|date=2020-04-22|publisher=[[端传媒|端传媒]]|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=zh|author=梁日恆|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808081231/https://theinitium.com/article/20200422-whatsnew-hksar-cabinet-reshuffle/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0" />、「大換血」<ref name=":4" />。

== 背景及經過 ==
林鄭月娥在2017年7月1日就任香港特別行政區行政長官後，支持度不斷下跌，市民不滿政府施政聲音日漸增加<ref>{{cite news|title=特首林鄭月娥民望vote Popularity of Chief Executive Carrie Lam Cheng Yuet Ngor|url=https://www.pori.hk/pop-poll/chief-executive/a003/satisfaction|accessdate=2020-10-27|work=[[香港民意研究所|香港民意研究所]]|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809185445/https://www.pori.hk/pop-poll/chief-executive/a003/satisfaction|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年3月，政府公佈的《[[2019年逃犯及刑事事宜相互法律協助法例（修訂）條例草案|逃犯條例修訂草案]]》觸發社會各界激烈反彈<ref>{{Cite news|title=點燃香港修例之爭的一樁謀殺案|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190619/hong-kong-murder-taiwan-extradition/zh-hant/|accessdate=2020-10-30|date=2019-06-19|last=Victor|first=Daniel|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]中文網|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2019-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807050608/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190619/hong-kong-murder-taiwan-extradition/zh-hant/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[「譴責鎮壓，撤回惡法」大遊行|引發近二百萬人在六月上街抗議]]，要求政府撤回法案<ref>{{Cite news|title=Hong Kong protest: 'Nearly two million' join demonstration|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-48656471|newspaper=[[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]]|date=2019-06-17|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015093026/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-48656471|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時有報導指，左派建議為挽救民意而棄車保帥，尤以有參與推行修例的[[香港特別行政區律政司司長|律政司司長]][[鄭若驊|鄭若驊]]最高危<ref>{{Cite news|title=【政情】林鄭表明不辭職 左派倡棄車保帥炒鄭若驊|url=https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353542|date=2019-06-28|accessdate=2020-10-26|work=[[Now新聞|Now新聞]]|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030093442/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353542|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[金融时报_(英国)|金融時報]]》曾引述知情人士透露，林鄭月娥在多個場合向北京政府提出請辭但都被拒<ref>{{Cite news|title=Hong Kong chief Carrie Lam offered to step down over protests|url=https://www.ft.com/content/e646dbba-a3e4-11e9-974c-ad1c6ab5efd1|accessdate=2020-10-26|date=2019-07-14|last=Liu|first=Nicolle|work=[[金融时报_(英国)|金融時報]]|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201070335/http://www.ft.com/content/e646dbba-a3e4-11e9-974c-ad1c6ab5efd1|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而[[路透社|路透社]]取得的錄音顯示，林鄭月娥曾表示，若情況允許的話她會離職<ref>{{Cite news|title=Special Report: Hong Kong leader says she would 'quit' if she could, fears her ability to resolve crisis now 'very limited'|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-carrielam-specialre-idUSKCN1VN1DU|newspaper=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2019-09-03|accessdate=2020-10-26|language=en|first=Greg|last=Torode|first2=James|last2=Pomfret|first3=Anne Marie|last3=Roantree|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025112630/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-carrielam-specialre-idUSKCN1VN1DU|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過林鄭均否認曾經提出請辭<ref>{{Cite news|title=【逃犯條例・短片】從未向中央請辭 林鄭否認「若可選擇第一件事會辭職」|date=2019-09-03|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190903/s00001/1567478142814/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87%e3%80%91%e5%be%9e%e6%9c%aa%e5%90%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e8%ab%8b%e8%be%ad-%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e5%90%a6%e8%aa%8d%e3%80%8c%e8%8b%a5%e5%8f%af%e9%81%b8%e6%93%87%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e4%bb%b6%e4%ba%8b%e6%9c%83%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7%e3%80%8d|accessdate=2020-10-26|work=[[明報|明報]]|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511103021/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190903/s00001/1567478142814/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87%e3%80%91%e5%be%9e%e6%9c%aa%e5%90%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e8%ab%8b%e8%be%ad-%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e5%90%a6%e8%aa%8d%e3%80%8c%e8%8b%a5%e5%8f%af%e9%81%b8%e6%93%87%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e4%bb%b6%e4%ba%8b%e6%9c%83%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7%e3%80%8d|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=【傳林鄭辭職】特首辦晚上回覆：林太從無辭職過|url=https://www.hk01.com/政情/351862/傳林鄭辭職-特首辦晚上回覆-林太從無辭職過|accessdate=2020-10-26|date=2019-07-14|author=沙半山|work=[[香港01|香港01]]|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714173501/https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/351862/%E5%82%B3%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E5%9B%9E%E8%A6%86-%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%AA%E5%BE%9E%E7%84%A1%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E9%81%8E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

